                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>
                        <additions>
                            <list>
                                <item xml:id="a1">
                                    <locus target="#2ra"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText"><ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT5920JohnBeg">Beginning of the Gospel of John</ref></desc>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a2">
                                    <locus target="#2va"/>
                                    <desc type="ScribalSupplication"/>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ብርዕ፡ ሠናይ፡ ዘተፈትነ፡ በዕለተ፡ ማክሰኞ፡ ኦእግዚኦ፡ አርትዕ፡ አፃብዕየ፡ ለጽሒፈ፡ መጽሐፍከ፡ ለወጢኖቱ፡ ወለፈጽሞቱ፡ አሠንያ፡ አግዚኦ፡
                                        በሥምረትከ፡ ለብርዕ፡ ታስተዳሉ፡ ማዕደ፡ ቃልከ፡ ውስተ፡ ጽርሕከ፡ ሰሌዳ፡ ኅድግ፡ ይቤለከ፡ </q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a3">
                                    <locus from="100va" to="102rb"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">Chronographical calculation of <foreign xml:lang="gez">maṭqǝʿ</foreign>, epact and other
                                        dates for the cycle of 7000 years.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ለመጥቅዕ፡ ወአበቅቴ፡ ለጰጕሜን፡ ወለመናፍቃን፡ ወለጥንትዮን፡ ለ፸፻፡ አመት፡ በበ፯ትገድሮ፡ ወለእመ፡ ገደፍኮ፡ በበ፯ትገድፎ፡ 
                                        እም፶፻ይወፅእ፡ ፪<t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a4">
                                    <locus from="102rb" to="102vb"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">Chronographical calculation on the length of the days and the nights of the twelve months of
                                        the year.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ሐሳብ፡ ዘመዓልት፡ ወሌሊት፡ ዘይነውህ፡ ወየሐጽር፡ በወርኃ፡ መስከረም፡ ፲፪መዓልቱ፡ ወ፲፪<pb n="102v"/>ሌሊት፡ ፪ሆሙ፡ ዕሩይ፡ 
                                        በወርኃ፡ ጥቅምት፡ ፲ወ፩፡ መዓልት፡ ፲፫፡ ሌ<add resp="Strelcyn">ሊት፡</add><t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a5">
                                    <locus from="100va" to="102rb"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">Chronographical calculation of Lent of Nineveh</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ወካዕበ፡ መጥቅዕ፡ በቀዳም፡ አመ፡ ኮነ፡ ፰ተ፡ ወስክ፡ ነነዌ፡ ትረክብ፡ በእሑድ፡ ፯፡ በሰኑይ፡ ፮፡ በሰሉስ፡ ፭፡ <t:gap xmlns:t="http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0" reason="ellipsis"/></q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="a6">
                                    <locus from="1r" to="1v"/>
                                    <desc type="GuestText">A fragment of <ref type="work" corresp="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1398Fethat">Fǝtḥat za-wald</ref> comparable to 
                                        <bibl corresp="http://zotero.org/groups/358366/items/K23J38IP"><seg type="book"><!-- attributes from original bibl--></seg><ptr target="bm:YabetaKrestiyanSalot1944"/><title level="m">የበተ፡ ክርስቲያን፡ ጸሎት፡ (Ya-beta krǝstiyān ṣalot, 'The Prayer of the Church')</title><pubPlace>ʾAddis Ababā</pubPlace><date>1943</date><citedRange>10</citedRange></bibl> written in a very 
                                        poor hand.</desc>
                                </item> 
                                <item xml:id="e1">
                                    <locus target="#100r"/>
                                    <desc type="OwnershipNote">The second owner 
                                        <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14330WaldaTaklaHaym">Walda Takla Hāymānot</persName> and the third 
                                        owner <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14331TasfaSeyon">Tasfā Ṣǝyon</persName> mentioned in a note.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="gez">ዝመጽሐፍ፡ ዘ<persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14331TasfaSeyon">ተሥፋ፡ ጽዮን፡</persName> ዘወኀቦ፡ 
                                        <persName role="owner" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/PRS14330WaldaTaklaHaym">ወልደ፡ ተክለ፡ ሃይማኖት፡</persName>ፍቁሩ።</q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e2">
                                    <desc type="PurchaseNote">A fragment of a printed sale catalogue is inserted after <locus target="#2"/> containing  
                                        erroneous information on the content of the codex.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="en"><foreign xml:lang="la">Liturgia Coptica.</foreign> Manuscript on Vellum, in a curious leather
                                        Pouch with Strap. 12mo. circa 1500 <add>Lawrence Sale v. 92£ A.a.</add></q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e3">
                                    <desc type="PurchaseNote">Note on the inner front cover, on a label.</desc>
                                    <q xml:lang="en">Ethiopic Liturgy - 4 Guineas - 305</q>
                                </item>
                                <item xml:id="e4">
                                    <locus target="#2ra #3v #4r #104v"/>
                                    <desc>Pen trials, scribbles.</desc>  
                                </item>
                            </list>
                        </additions>
